{"tid":1008704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角警方食環駐重兵 小販稱凌晨後方准開爐","createTime":"2019-02-04T16:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T06:26:39.000Z","uid":66260,"like":7,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"c8fce01bf71d3173e340437e59383cad644b3656","tid":1008704,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190204/59224877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F59224877&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=553e78b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F59224877&h=88451c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190204/59224877</a><br />\n3年前大年初一深夜，旺角街頭爆發大規模警民衝突，警方今年年三十晚繼續在旺角街頭駐重兵，西洋菜南街至少停泊10輛警車和食環小巴，每個路口均有十多名警務人員和食環署人員駐守，並掛起「農曆新年期間，切勿阻礙通道，以免發生危險」等標語。<br />\n<br />\n砵蘭街街頭則有數十檔小販擺設燒肉、燒海鮮等熟食檔，惟至晚上10時半仍全部都未開爐。有小販向記者稱，警方稱凌晨12時後才可開爐，故小販都在街頭擺檔等待，警員和食環署人員亦未有干涉。<br />\n<br />\n有小販疑似「偷雞」提早開爐，即時有警員上前勸阻：「乖啦，熄咗佢啦，未夠鐘呀。」  <br />\n<br />\n點解要12點先可以開爐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e66c83a7d591a6d17c0dcab206664206f25bfa8","tid":1008704,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd35251129d62f4450e5724c666307980257036e","tid":1008704,"uid":9328,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"12點後 黑 ..... 話事"},{"pid":"285ffef6d792eda5a4264aa93948382571757912","tid":1008704,"uid":9193,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乖啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"56b7a664fa68148839bd6c685b6df60d0114abd3","tid":1008704,"uid":53466,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:26:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"014dfbb3da36c613396512770338540d36319aef","tid":1008704,"uid":146604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"12點夠鐘收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee62943ebc3ee66f18e8427cd04fad75a54e9ea9","tid":1008704,"uid":49918,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a3225114e4ba8df3e05a2e38faab99a2d622442","tid":1008704,"uid":10757,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNMTQZ4Ftnc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRNMTQZ4Ftnc&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=09c89922\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNMTQZ4Ftnc</a><br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"78a321c6d7c05004569f221618093a69726f5919","tid":1008704,"uid":136089,"like":0,"dislike